      "message": "Assertion failed: TypeOK \u2014 /\\ json_mode         \\in BOOLEAN\n    /\\ query_constructed \\in BOOLEAN\n    /\\ stdout_written    \\in BOOLEAN\n    /\\ res...",
      "description": "Test assertion for TypeOK from RunReviewPassAutoFix spec"
    }
